---
import ContentLayout from '../../layouts/ContentLayout.astro';
import cities from '../../data/cities.json';

export function getStaticPaths() {
  const allCities = [
    ...cities.uk.map(c => ({ ...c, country: 'UK' })),
    ...cities.us.map(c => ({ ...c, country: 'US' })),
  ];
  return allCities.map(city => ({
    params: { city: city.slug },
    props: { city },
  }));
}

const { city } = Astro.props;
const isUK = city.country === 'UK';
const currency = isUK ? '£' : '$';
const currencyWord = isUK ? 'GBP' : 'USD';

const title = `Website Audit Services in ${city.name} | Professional SEO Audit`;
const description = `Get a professional website audit in ${city.name}, ${city.region}. Our 72-checkpoint analysis covers SEO, technical, content, UX, and security. Pricing from ${currency}297.`;

const toc = [
  { label: `Why ${city.name} Businesses Need Website Audits`, id: 'why' },
  { label: 'What Our Audit Covers', id: 'covers' },
  { label: 'Our Audit Process', id: 'process' },
  { label: 'Common Issues We Find', id: 'issues' },
  { label: 'Pricing', id: 'pricing' },
  { label: 'Get Started', id: 'get-started' },
];

const schema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'Service',
  name: `Website Audit Service in ${city.name}`,
  provider: {
    '@type': 'Organization',
    name: 'AuditWeb',
    url: 'https://auditweb.site',
  },
  areaServed: {
    '@type': 'City',
    name: city.name,
  },
  description: description,
  priceRange: `${currency}297-${currency}997`,
};
---

<ContentLayout
  title={title}
  description={description}
  breadcrumbs={[
    { label: 'Website Audit', href: '/website-audit/' },
    { label: 'Services', href: '/website-audit-services/' },
    { label: city.name, href: `/website-audit-services/${city.slug}/` },
  ]}
  toc={toc}
  schema={schema}
  showLeadForm={true}
  publishDate="2026-03-28"
>
  <h2 id="why">Why {city.name} Businesses Need Website Audits</h2>
  <p>{city.intro}</p>
  <p>Whether you're a local service business, an e-commerce store, or a growing startup, your website is your most important marketing asset. A professional audit reveals the hidden issues that prevent your site from ranking, converting, and generating revenue.</p>
  <p>Businesses in {city.name} face competition from both local rivals and national brands targeting the {city.region} market. A website audit gives you the data-driven insights to outperform them both — identifying exactly what to fix, in what order, for maximum impact.</p>

  <h2 id="covers">What Our Audit Covers</h2>
  <p>Our comprehensive 72-checkpoint audit examines every aspect of your website:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>SEO Analysis:</strong> Keyword targeting, title tags, meta descriptions, heading structure, internal linking, content quality, and schema markup. We check how well your site is optimised for the searches your {city.name} customers are making.</li>
    <li><strong>Technical Review:</strong> Crawlability, indexation, site architecture, Core Web Vitals, mobile-friendliness, HTTPS configuration, and structured data validation.</li>
    <li><strong>Content Evaluation:</strong> Content quality, topical coverage, thin content identification, duplicate content, and content gap analysis against your competitors.</li>
    <li><strong>UX Assessment:</strong> Navigation usability, mobile experience, form functionality, conversion paths, and accessibility compliance.</li>
    <li><strong>Security Check:</strong> SSL configuration, security headers, software vulnerabilities, and data protection compliance.</li>
    <li><strong>Performance Analysis:</strong> Page speed, server response time, image optimisation, code efficiency, and third-party script impact.</li>
    <li><strong>Competitive Benchmarking:</strong> How your website compares to your top {city.name} competitors across all these dimensions.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="process">Our Audit Process</h2>
  <ol>
    <li><strong>Discovery:</strong> You share your website URL, business goals, and target audience. We configure our audit tools specifically for your site.</li>
    <li><strong>Analysis:</strong> Our team runs the full 72-checkpoint audit using industry-leading tools including Screaming Frog, Ahrefs, Google Search Console data, and PageSpeed Insights.</li>
    <li><strong>Report:</strong> We compile findings into a clear, prioritised report with specific fix instructions for each issue. Every recommendation includes expected impact and implementation difficulty.</li>
    <li><strong>Strategy Call:</strong> For Comprehensive and Enterprise audits, we walk you through the findings in a 30-minute video call, answer questions, and help you plan implementation.</li>
    <li><strong>Support:</strong> We're available for follow-up questions as you implement the recommendations. Our reports are designed to be actionable whether your team implements internally or you hire developers.</li>
  </ol>

  <h2 id="issues">Common Issues We Find in {city.name}</h2>
  <p>Across hundreds of audits for {city.region} businesses, these are the most common issues we discover:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Slow page speed:</strong> Many {city.name} business websites score below 50 on Google's mobile speed test, losing visitors who won't wait more than 3 seconds for a page to load.</li>
    <li><strong>Poor mobile experience:</strong> With over 60% of local searches happening on mobile, a site that doesn't work well on phones is losing the majority of potential customers.</li>
    <li><strong>Missing local SEO signals:</strong> No Google Business Profile optimisation, inconsistent NAP (Name, Address, Phone) across directories, and missing local schema markup.</li>
    <li><strong>Thin service pages:</strong> Service pages with 100-200 words of generic content that don't demonstrate expertise or address customer questions.</li>
    <li><strong>No conversion optimisation:</strong> Websites that get traffic but don't convert because CTAs are buried, forms are too long, or trust signals are missing.</li>
    <li><strong>Outdated security:</strong> Missing SSL certificates, outdated CMS versions, and no security headers — putting both data and rankings at risk.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="pricing">Pricing</h2>
  <p>Our audit packages for {city.name} businesses:</p>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Package</th>
        <th>Price</th>
        <th>Best For</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Basic Audit</strong></td>
        <td>{currency}297</td>
        <td>Small sites under 50 pages</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Comprehensive Audit</strong></td>
        <td>{currency}997</td>
        <td>Growing businesses, e-commerce stores</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><strong>Enterprise</strong></td>
        <td>Custom</td>
        <td>Large sites, multi-location businesses</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <p>All packages include our 100% money-back guarantee: if we don't identify at least {currency}10,000 in potential revenue improvements, you pay nothing.</p>

  <h2 id="get-started">Get Started</h2>
  <p>Ready to find out what's holding your {city.name} website back? Fill in the form to request your audit. We'll review your site and send your report within 48 hours.</p>
  <p>Alternatively, try our <a href="/free-website-audit/">free instant audit tool</a> for a quick health check before committing to a full professional audit.</p>
</ContentLayout>
